in keeping a tight lid
on this investigation.

28
00:02:40,852 --> 00:02:42,396
- [Reporter] Sir, how
much is the ransom

29
00:02:42,396 --> 00:02:43,648
and how will the
payment be handled?

30
00:02:43,691 --> 00:02:47,691
Well, as of this moment, we
