have a suspect, don't you?

32
00:02:50,737 --> 00:02:51,447
What?

33
00:02:51,447 --> 00:02:52,531
What are you babbling about?

34
00:02:52,531 --> 00:02:54,783
A man named Aragami
has contacted my paper.

35
00:02:54,883 --> 00:02:58,883
He claims that he is
responsible for this crime.

36
00:02:58,883 --> 00:03:02,748
Did you know that, sir?

37
00:03:02,748 --> 00:03:03,749
(all gasping)

38
00:03:03,849 --> 00:03:07,849
Ms. Takeuchi!

39
00:03:09,536 --> 00:03:13,536
Wrong door.

40
