43
00:03:22,672 --> 00:03:26,672
Momiji, how could you get lost?

44
00:03:26,672 --> 00:03:28,984
I was standing
right next to you.

45
00:03:28,984 --> 00:03:31,279
I said I was sorry.

46
00:03:31,279 --> 00:03:32,196
Ah, come on, Ryouko.

47
00:03:32,282 --> 00:03:36,282
She may be a princess, but
she's still just a kid.

48
00:03:36,282 --> 00:03:37,951
Then again, give her five years

49
00:03:37,951 --> 00:03:41,706
