51
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:44,709
Lecher!

52
00:03:44,709 --> 00:03:46,042
Do you have to make
a pass at everyone?

53
00:03:46,142 --> 00:03:50,142
Oh, do you always have to
resort to violence, Ryouko?

54
00:03:50,142 --> 00:03:51,424
You're a wimp.

55
00:03:51,424 --> 00:03:53,925
I just prefer brains over brawn.

56
00:03:53,925 --> 00:03:55,885
Excuse me.

57
00:03:55,885 --> 00:03:57,803
Oh, I haven't introduced myself.

58
00:03:57,803 --> 00:04:00,433
Shunichi Sugishita's the
name, General Manager

59
00:04:00,433 --> 00:04:03,561
