Managers at my age.

63
00:04:12,194 --> 00:04:12,818
Wow.

64
00:04:12,818 --> 00:04:13,654
Don't be impressed.

65
00:04:13,654 --> 00:04:17,073
Sugi's Section is where
metro damps all the losers.

66
00:04:17,073 --> 00:04:17,823
